      <title>穆迪将中国开发商万科评级下调至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-12/moody-s-cuts-china-developer-vanke-cut-to-junk-territory-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对其偿债能力的担忧日益加剧，国有开发商万科集团一直面临压力，穆迪评级将其信用评级下调至垃圾级。斯蒂芬·恩格尔在彭博电视台进行报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-12/moody-s-cuts-china-developer-vanke-cut-to-junk-territory-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 02:35:07 GMT</pubDate>
